## Context

- hla-peptide-presentation-modeling: Implemented core Phase 1-4 pipeline modules
  - HLA allele panel (hla_allele_panel.json): 9 alleles, 3 susceptibility, 2 protective, 2 control, 2 Class I
  - GAS proteome manifest: symlinked 6 serotypes from gas-molecular-mimicry-mapping. M5/M18 from UniParc (no VF annotation)
